compat-change.description: Remove meta-reflection workaround for hidden api usage for apps targeting R+. This allowed apps to obtain references to blacklisted fields and methods through an extra layer of reflection.
compat-change.name: PREVENT_META_REFLECTION_BLACKLIST_ACCESS

compat-change.description: Gates whether calls to {@link #getHardwareAddress()} made by non-system processes to return the actual MAC address (pre-change behavior) or an anonymized MAC address (post-change behavior). Future versions of Android will enforce the post-change behavior through SELinux.
compat-change.name: ANONYMIZED_DEVICE_ADDRESS_CHANGE_ID
